msgid "Dimensions"
msgstr "Dimensiones"

msgid "Internal vs External Dimensions:"
msgstr "Dimensiones internas vs. externas:"

msgid ""
"• <strong>Internal dimensions</strong> are used for packing algorithm "
"calculations (determining what fits inside)"
msgstr ""
"• <strong>Dimensiones internas</strong> se utilizan para cálculos del "
"algoritmo de empaque (determinar qué cabe dentro)"

msgid ""
"• <strong>Wall thickness</strong> defines the package material thickness "
"(default 0.5cm for standard cardboard)"
msgstr ""
"• <strong>Grosor de la pared</strong> define el grosor del material del "
"paquete (por defecto 0.5cm para cartón estándar)"

msgid ""
"• <strong>External dimensions</strong> are automatically calculated and sent "
"to shipping carriers for rate calculations"
msgstr ""
"• <strong>Dimensiones externas</strong> se calculan automáticamente y se "
"envían a los transportistas de envío para cálculos de tarifas"

